---
title: Mexican Style Cottage Pie with Sweet Potato and Mozzarella
description: What makes a pie a pie? We know some people who insist it must have a 'pastry hat and coat' to qualify. But what about a cottage pie? Surely that counts too, even though it's topped with potato. And what about this cottage pie? We've given it a HelloFresh twist with Fajita spices and a sweet potato crown. Whether it still qualifies for official pie status, there's no denying it's tasty!
